OL,3,CMore than 25,000 hours lost in one
OL,4,Cmonth due to ambulance handover delays
OL,6,FThe measures were put in place for two
OL,7,Fdays as bosses felt there was "a great
OL,8,Frisk" of patient harm due to extremely
OL,9,Fhigh demand and handover delays
OL,10,Foutside hospitals. Widespread flooding
OL,11,Facross the East Midlands also slowed
OL,12,Fdown crew response times.
OL,14,FThe meeting was held to discuss what
OL,15,Fcaused problems and what plans are in
OL,16,Fplace to improve the situation.
