OL,3,CMore than 25,000 hours lost in one
OL,4,Cmonth due to ambulance handover delays
OL,6,F"The whole year has been challenging
OL,7,Fin terms of what we've faced but
OL,8,Fparticularly over the past two months
OL,9,Fit's been very pressurised over the
OL,10,Fwhole of the health system".
OL,12,FMr Holdaway says handover delays are a
OL,13,Fsystem-wide issue and any solution
OL,14,Fmust also be approached in that way.
OL,16,F"It's just as important to get the
OL,17,Fpatients out of hospital to enable us
OL,18,Fto get them in the front door and
OL,19,Fworking on that flow together as a
OL,20,Fsystem is the only way to fix the
OL,21,Fissue", he adds.
