OL,3,CMore than 25,000 hours lost in one
OL,4,Cmonth due to ambulance handover delays
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the average pre-handover
OL,7,Ftime reached 55 minutes - More than
OL,8,Fthree times the national target of 15
OL,9,Fminutes.
OL,11,F"People ring 999 and the expectation
OL,12,Fis we're going to be there. Human
OL,13,Fnature is they want the ambulance
OL,14,Fthere and then and if they don't get
OL,15,Fit then people are going to quite
OL,16,Frightly ask why. This isn't the
OL,17,Fservice we want to provide - we want
OL,18,Fto get to patients quicker", says Mr
OL,19,FHoldaway.
